### My Experience with jQuery
So far I really like jQuery. I'm using it and a pagination extension to scroll
through table rows. It can do way more than that though.

### jQuery Examples
#### Document
The helpful document ready setup:

    $(document).ready(function() {
    // Do stuff here...
    });

#### Selectors

    $("#mydiv").css("color","red");

### AJAX

Example from [[/PBooks]]:

~~~
$.ajax({
    type: "POST",
    url: "x--invoice-paid",
    data: {
        'invoice_number': invoice_number,
        'entry_id': entry_id
    },
    success: function (res){
        $("#p_"+invoice_number).replaceWith("Paid");
    }
});
~~~

